---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Jamail Hardwoods – Terms & Conditions"
  description="Jamail Hardwoods Terms & Conditions, including SMS terms and customer communication policies."
>
  <Header />

  <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-brand-ivory py-14 sm:py-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-b from-brand-sand/70 via-brand-ivory to-white pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto rounded-3xl bg-white/90 backdrop-blur p-6 sm:p-10 shadow-soft">
        <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-tight text-brand-ink">
          Jamail Hardwoods – Terms & Conditions
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm sm:text-base text-brand-ink/70">Last updated: November 2025</p>

        <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-brand-ink/85 leading-relaxed">
          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
            <p>
              By accessing or using the website
              <a href="https://jamailfloors.com" class="text-brand-brass underline" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer"> https://jamailfloors.com</a>
              ("Website") or by contacting Jamail Hardwoods for services, you agree to these Terms & Conditions.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 font-semibold">Required 10DLC Statement:</p>
            <p>
              By providing your phone number and opting in, you agree to receive SMS messages from Jamail Hardwoods and
              accept our Privacy Policy.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">2. About Jamail Hardwoods</h2>
            <p>
              Jamail Hardwoods is a flooring and curated finishes showroom based in Houston, Texas, offering hardwood,
              tile, and design services to homeowners, designers, and builders.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">3. Website Use</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Do not interfere with website functionality or security.</li>
              <li>Do not provide false or misleading information.</li>
              <li>Do not attempt unauthorized access to our systems.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">4. Product Information, Quotes & Orders</h2>
            <p>
              Product information, stock, pricing, sample availability, and specifications may change at any time.
              Quotes are not final until confirmed by a Jamail Hardwoods representative.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">5. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
            <p>
              The Website is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind regarding accuracy, availability, or
              performance.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p>
              Jamail Hardwoods is not liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from use of the
              Website or services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">7. SMS Terms & Conditions</h2>
            <p>
              By opting in, you agree to receive SMS messages from Jamail Hardwoods at +1 (832) 930-5936. Consent is not
              a condition of purchase.
            </p>
            <p class="mt-3 font-semibold">Required 10DLC Statement:</p>
            <p>
              By providing your phone number and opting in, you agree to receive SMS messages from Jamail Hardwoods and
              accept our Privacy Policy.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">7.1 Types of Messages You Will Receive</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Appointment confirmations</li>
              <li>Order updates</li>
              <li>Delivery notifications</li>
              <li>General customer service messages</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">7.2 Message Frequency</h2>
            <p>
              Message frequency varies, but you may receive up to 4 messages per month. Message and data rates may apply.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">7.3 How to Get Help</h2>
            <p>Text HELP for assistance.</p>
            <p>You may also contact us at +1 (832) 930-5936 or info@jamailfloors.com.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">7.4 How to Opt Out</h2>
            <p>Text STOP at any time to unsubscribe. You will receive a confirmation message.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">7.5 Data Use and Sharing</h2>
            <p>
              We do not share your mobile number, SMS consent, or opt-in information with any third parties, except
              where required by law.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">7.6 Privacy Policy Link</h2>
            <p>You can review our full privacy policy at:</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">7.7 Sample SMS Messages</h2>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-sand/40 p-4">
                <p class="font-semibold">Sample 1:</p>
                <p class="mt-1">Jamail Hardwoods: Your appointment is confirmed for 2026. Text STOP to unsubscribe. Text HELP for assistance.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-sand/40 p-4">
                <p class="font-semibold">Sample 2:</p>
                <p class="mt-1">Jamail Hardwoods: Your order #[number] is ready for pickup/delivery. Text STOP to unsubscribe.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-sand/40 p-4">
                <p class="font-semibold">Sample 3:</p>
                <p class="mt-1">Jamail Hardwoods: Your sample request has been received. We will notify you when it ships. Text STOP to unsubscribe.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">8. Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p>
              All content on this Website is owned by Jamail Hardwoods and may not be copied without permission.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">9. Third-Party Links</h2>
            <p>
              We are not responsible for content or policies on any external websites linked from our site.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">10. Changes to These Terms</h2>
            <p>
              We may update these Terms & Conditions at any time. The updated date will be shown at the top of this page.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">11. Governing Law</h2>
            <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the State of Texas.</p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-heading text-2xl mb-3">12. Contact Information</h2>
            <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-sand/40 p-5">
              <p class="font-semibold">Jamail Hardwoods</p>
              <p>2643 Colquitt St</p>
              <p>Houston, TX 77098</p>
              <p class="mt-3">Phone & SMS Support: <a href="tel:+18329305936" class="text-brand-brass underline">+1 (832) 930-5936</a></p>
              <p>Email: <a href="mailto:info@jamailfloors.com" class="text-brand-brass underline">info@jamailfloors.com</a></p>
            </div>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
